               <code code="51945-4" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="PACKAGE LABEL.PRINCIPAL DISPLAY PANEL"/>
               <title>NITROUS OXIDE USP LABEL</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>NITROUS OXIDE U.S.P.  UN 1070  NON-FLAMMABLE-2  OXIDIZER-5.1</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>ADMINISTRATION OF NITROUS OXIDE MAY BE HAZARDOUS OR CONTRAINDICATED.  FOR USE ONLY BY OR UNDER THE SUPERVISION OF A LICENSED PRACTITIONER WHO IS EXPERIENCED IN THE USE AND ADMINISTRATION OF NITROUS OXIDE AND IS FAMILIAR WITH THE INDICATIONS, EFFECTS, DOSAGES, METHODS, METHODS, AND FREQUENCY AND DURATION OF ADMINISTRATION AND WITH THE HAZARDS, CONTRAINDICATIONS AND SIDE EFFECTS AND THE PRECAUTIONS TO BE TAKEN.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>CAUTION: Rx ONLY.  FEDERAL LAW PROHIBITS DISPENSING WITHOUT A PRESCRIPTION.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>GROSS WT________________ LBS____________ OZ</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>TARE WT ________________ LBS ______________ OZ</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>NET WT. _________________ LBS _______________ OZ</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>SIZE _______________ CONTENTS___________LITERS_____________</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>7025R1  5/04</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="CGINITROUS1"/>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20100101"/>
